{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "鐵人三項", "storyInfo": "鼠膽龍威隊順利突破跑步環節。\n詩懷雅和星熊聊起了海中央的游輪以及主持人的身份。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$emperor_intro", "key": "$emperor_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然在比賽之初就被其他隊伍盯上，但是鼠膽龍威隊再次上演了一場精彩的突圍。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$phonevibration", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潘喬先生，您在第一輪中提到了這支隊伍的配合問題，那現在您怎麼看？", "name": "D.D.D."}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_192_1#1", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "配合問題不是一夜之間就能解決的。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過很明顯，這兩個人自己也知道這個問題，所以她們在戰鬥中很明顯有了分工。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一次，比第一輪裡的戰鬥，要俐落許多。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "原來如此，也就是說，他們獲勝的機率變得更高了嗎？", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還不好說，其他選手也會有自己的對策。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說的也是，普通的阻攔對鼠膽龍威隊已經不生效了，讓我們期待一下其他選手會不會有什麼新招吧！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，說得沒錯。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且她們之間氣氛也緩和了一點，不知道是不是發生了什麼。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "居然是伊比利亞時代的產物，怪不得......", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？Missy，你不看比賽在看什麼呢？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在看這艘遊輪的資訊。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼有趣的嗎，你剛才好像說到伊比利亞？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，這艘船，其實前身是伊比利亞時期留下的東西。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼早？......不過仔細想想，除了伊比利亞，確實好像應該沒別的國家有這種東西。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且這艘船還是坎黛拉市長花了重金再從伊比利亞人手上買來技術改造出來的。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而做這些只是為了讓這艘船在這座城市的海上漂著。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這片大地上我覺得都不會再有第二個人這麼做了。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那確實是奢侈到一定境界了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說到這個，Missy，你不是這兩天在研究這個市長，有什麼結論嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "結論......其實還挺簡單的。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個坎黛拉·桑切斯，在某種意義上，是能和魏長官比肩的人物。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有這麼厲害？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有。雖然方向完全不同，但他們都是胸中完全裝下了自己的城市，完完全全握住了城市的韁繩的人。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "作為龍門近衛局的一員，我絕對不會說我佩服建造了這樣一座城市的人。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是作為詩懷雅家的女兒，我也必須承認，建造了這樣一座城市的人非常厲害。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果說這座城市根基要遠比它表現的那樣更穩固，那麼這座城市的上層建築就比它表現得還要瘋狂。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三方政府的人每天都在湧入這座城市，新聞上也偶爾會有他們發生爭執甚至發生小規模衝突的報導。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，沒有人在乎。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們秘密而又公開地來到這裡，遵守著心照不宣的規則，在這裡享受著他們在外面無法享受到的樂趣。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能想像嗎？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當三方中有人第一次在這裡發生衝突時，一定是坎黛拉市長出面，用我們誰都無法想像的方法“說服”了他們。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並且在那之後，任何人來到這座城市，都必須遵守她定下的規則。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我不知道那是什麼，一些把柄？還是政治籌碼？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉女士手上有能夠保護這座城市的武裝力量，這是肯定的。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是在那之上，我覺得答案很簡單啊，Missy，你不是已經發現了嗎？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是什麼啊？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就是——酒，糖，咖啡，還有娛樂。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#2"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些東西怎麼可能......", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老話說得好啊，Missy，由儉入奢易。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說嬌生慣養的老爺們，就算是我，忽然要我失去一個我已經習慣了而且覺得很好的東西，我也會很難受。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更不要說一旦失去後，我就只能再去忍受那些破爛。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人的意志在有些時候是很軟弱的，更不要說玻利瓦爾變成現在這樣，你跟我說這裡有許多意志堅定的人，我是不信的。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一開始肯定沒有那麼順利，但是久而久之，沒有人能夠站出來否定這一切，這一切也就成為了某種理所當然。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#2"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我也承認，能在一開始就決定將這座城市變成如今這副樣貌，這個市長確實非常厲害。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#2"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#6"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "厲害到令人害怕的程度。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#6"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G03"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前面有個彎道，走近道？", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有必要，從地圖來看，騎行階段近道才多，即使有人想搞事，也應該是那時候的事。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別忘了，近道裡埋伏著大量坎黛拉女士的手下，這些人可能比危險分子還要危險。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對方第一輪都沒有出手的話，我想，第二輪他們只會更加謹慎。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，走一步看一步吧。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來，Missy，這個主持人你眼不眼熟？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？你這麼一說，好像確實在哪裡見過。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我也覺得在哪裡見過。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她是D.D.D.啊。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "D.D.D.？哦，我想起來了，不是那個很有名的DJ嗎，我看過海報。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她怎麼跑來當主持人了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？你是......鑄鐵？你怎麼在這裡，出任務？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算是吧。我們在玻利瓦爾出任務，順便協助艾雅法拉做一些地質考察，聽說這裡有座城市，就在完事後申請了一個假期過來。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#8"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們呢？和陳一起來的嗎？", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是，我們是因為別的原因來的。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你好像挺熟的，你也喜歡聽音樂？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是，幹員裡有不少她的粉絲，我也就耳濡目染了一些。對了，要過來和我們坐一起嗎？", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#1"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼說，Missy？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#1"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啊。我正嫌比賽有點無聊呢。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "艾雅法拉也來了？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#7"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#7", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊，這次就是想讓她也放鬆一下才來的。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#8"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#8", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，我一直沒見過她，這次可要好好見一見。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}